00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:15,110
Leader Li of the Fortress
of the Forty-Eight,

374
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:16,910
the son of the Mountain Sword,

375
00:25:16,910 --> 00:25:18,360
the daughter of General Wu Fei

376
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,510
and Huo Liantao of Huo’s Manor.

377
00:25:21,110 --> 00:25:22,750
Some are martial artists

378
00:25:22,750 --> 00:25:23,890
while some are not.

379
00:25:24,630 --> 00:25:25,550
Some are good

380
00:25:26,510 --> 00:25:27,660
and some are bad.

381
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,870
But none of them knows

382
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,370
what the ripple pattern stands for.

383
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:38,260
Perhaps

384
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:40,990
those who buried
The Color of Ocean and Heaven

385
00:25:40,990 --> 00:25:42,990
decided to end everything with them.

386
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,330
Or maybe

387
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:47,890
they intended to protect their children.

388
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:53,730
Anyway, that pattern is passed down,

389
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:56,570
but The Color of Ocean and Heaven
remains a mystery.

390
00:25:59,230 --> 00:26:00,070
Master,

391
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:04,280
I’ve taken the third herb.

392
00:26:06,870 --> 00:26:08,910
Do I have a few more months to live?

393
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,910
A year at most

394
00:26:12,910 --> 00:26:15,360
without using your energy.

395
00:26:16,750 --> 00:26:18,630
Otherwise...

396
00:26:20,270 --> 00:26:21,870
Life and death are inseparable.

397
00:26:21,870 --> 00:26:23,960
All roads lead to the inevitable

398
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:25,510
as we can only live 100 years tops.

399
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:27,390
Death is only a matter of time.

400
00:26:28,230 --> 00:26:29,680
No need to bother ourselves with it.

401
00:26:30,200 --> 00:26:32,510
I’m glad you can think like that.

402
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:43,360
Master.

403
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:45,360
I’m thinking

404
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:48,050
to go out for a trip.

405
00:26:49,390 --> 00:26:50,910
Is there something else
you’d like to do?

406
00:26:51,910 --> 00:26:53,560
I haven’t got to

407
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:55,080
take Fei to Jiankang

408
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,870
to introduce my hometown to her.

409
00:27:02,320 --> 00:27:03,690
It’s now

410
00:27:05,230 --> 00:27:06,870
or never.

411
00:27:06,870 --> 00:27:08,480
This isn’t like

412
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:10,270
any other trips before.

413
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:11,840
Do not

414
00:27:13,390 --> 00:27:15,110
push yourself too hard.

415
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,870
I understand.

416
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:36,200
Weed Spirit.

417
00:27:40,630 --> 00:27:42,080
Let’s go.

418
00:28:13,230 --> 00:28:15,270
You’re back, Sheng.

419
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:18,110
I’m here. Isn’t that obvious?

420
00:28:18,630 --> 00:28:21,200
Are you leaving again so soon?

421
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:22,270
I’m needed

422
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:23,800
for some business outside.

423
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,150
What business?

424
00:28:25,150 --> 00:28:26,030
I heard

425
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:28,320
you’re taking others with you.

426
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:33,030
It’s about the secret service.

427
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:34,030
Nothing serious.

428
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:37,440
Fei has just left,
and you will leave, too.

429
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,200
No.

430
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:39,680
Let me go with you.

431
00:28:41,150 --> 00:28:42,360
Look,

432
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:43,990
Fei is already out

433
00:28:43,990 --> 00:28:45,270
and I’ll be leaving soon.

434
00:28:45,270 --> 00:28:47,870
Someone needs to hold the fort.

435
00:28:48,150 --> 00:28:49,840
You should stay

436
00:28:49,840 --> 00:28:51,360
and watch the house.

437
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:54,510
It’s boring.

438
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,990
I’m not a watchdog, am I?

439
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:59,100
<i>Liu’s Manor Invitation</i>

440
00:28:59,480 --> 00:29:00,750
What is this?

441
00:29:01,580 --> 00:29:02,460
<i>Liu’s Manor Invitation</i>

442
00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:09,720
Lord Liu of Liu’s Manor

443
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:12,150
is celebrating his mother’s birthday.

444
00:29:12,150 --> 00:29:14,270
I’ll drop a visit to them.

445
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,600
No big deal.

446
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:16,910
Really?

447
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,750
Why are there so many invitations?

448
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:21,230
Is there also one for me?

449
00:29:23,910 --> 00:29:25,030
Lord Liu

450
00:29:25,030 --> 00:29:26,480
loves making friends.

451
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,840
All the invitations

452
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:29,480
are for our members.

453
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,030
They’ve already been taken.

454
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:33,480
Fine.

455
00:29:34,150 --> 00:29:35,110
By the way,

456
00:29:36,030 --> 00:29:38,320
how’s Chuchu been lately?

457
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:40,390
She’s been at home

458
00:29:40,390 --> 00:29:42,630
studying martial arts manuals.

459
00:29:42,990 --> 00:29:44,840
That’s even more boring.

460
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:00,750
Chuchu.

461
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:02,230
Madam.

462
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:05,510
I’ve read the manual

463
00:30:05,510 --> 00:30:06,270
of the Xiaoxiang Sect you put together.

464
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:07,440
It’s well-organized.

465
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,990
I’ve also clarified

466
00:30:08,990 --> 00:30:10,200
a few vague descriptions.

467
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,390
You can have another look.

468
00:30:11,390 --> 00:30:12,840
Thank you.

469
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,870
I thought Yan

470
00:30:13,870 --> 00:30:16,150
showed it to seniors
of the Xiaoxiang Sect.

471
00:30:16,150 --> 00:30:17,960
I didn’t mean to trouble you.

472
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,630
We’re a family.

473
00:30:19,630 --> 00:30:21,720
No trouble at all.

474
00:30:21,720 --> 00:30:23,800
I’ve handed all my work

475
00:30:23,800 --> 00:30:25,230
to the younger generation

476
00:30:25,230 --> 00:30:26,870
and have more free time now.

477
00:30:27,870 --> 00:30:30,600
I’m surprised

478
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:31,480
that a delicate

479
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:33,560
well-bred girl like you

480
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:35,030
would do such an amazing job

481
00:30:35,030 --> 00:30:37,200
in compiling martial arts manuals.

482
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,630
I’m flattered.

483
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:41,560
Members of the Fortress
all have their duties.

484
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:43,480
I can read

485
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:45,200
and write,

486
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:47,800
and I’m interested in martial arts,

487
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:49,630
so I’m only trying to

488
00:30:49,630 --> 00:30:50,840
put all I have into good use.

489
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:52,800
That’s too modest of you.

490
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:54,150
Organizing such manuals

491
00:30:54,150 --> 00:30:55,990
requires profound knowledge,

492
00:30:55,990 --> 00:30:57,360
persistence

493
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:59,200
and selfless dedication.

494
00:30:59,200 --> 00:31:00,910
Few can be

495
00:31:00,910 --> 00:31:01,600
a better fit than you

496
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,910
for the job.

497
00:31:04,990 --> 00:31:06,510
Chuchu,

498
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:10,360
my father devoted himself
to the Snow-breaking Blade.

499
00:31:10,360 --> 00:31:12,320
He only accomplished

500
00:31:12,320 --> 00:31:14,440
Edgeless out of the three moves

501
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:16,630
and failed to master the nine skills,

502
00:31:16,630 --> 00:31:18,800
so he didn’t leave any manuals behind.

503
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:20,390
I was with him all the time

504
00:31:20,390 --> 00:31:22,150
and picked up a few things.

505
00:31:22,510 --> 00:31:23,910
I want you

506
00:31:23,910 --> 00:31:25,630
to sort them out.

507
00:31:25,840 --> 00:31:27,110
Can I?

508
00:31:27,320 --> 00:31:28,600
You won’t be disappointed.

509
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:29,630
I’ll do my best

510
00:31:29,630 --> 00:31:31,630
and get it done soon.

511
00:31:31,630 --> 00:31:33,030
But

512
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:35,110
it may take a while before I can begin

513
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:36,870
as I have an appointment with Lord Liu

514
00:31:36,870 --> 00:31:38,360
to consult him

515
00:31:38,360 --> 00:31:40,080
about certain skills
on the Double Ninth Festival.

516
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,720
Go ahead. No problem.

517
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:44,840
As long as you don’t pick a fight,

518
00:31:44,840 --> 00:31:46,870
skills you’ve learned

519
00:31:46,870 --> 00:31:48,870
are enough to protect yourself.

520
00:31:48,870 --> 00:31:50,360
Just be careful.

521
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,440
I will.

522
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,800
Thank you.

523
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:53,910
I’m leaving.

524
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:06,600
Sheng.

525
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:07,510
Aunt.

526
00:32:07,510 --> 00:32:08,810
What are you doing here?

527
00:32:10,800 --> 00:32:13,150
To go to the library.

528
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:19,360
For books or the person there?

529
00:32:22,910 --> 00:32:24,030
Sheng,

530
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:26,960
Miss Wu’s father was a warrior.

531
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:29,030
After he left, she stays with us alone

532
00:32:29,510 --> 00:32:30,910
but she’s tough

533
00:32:30,910 --> 00:32:32,480
and strong.

534
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:34,360
If you like her,

535
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:36,630
don’t ever hurt her, understand?

536
00:32:39,030 --> 00:32:40,440
You have my word.

537
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:43,030
I’ll always cherish her

538
00:32:43,030 --> 00:32:46,230
and won’t bring shame on our Fortress.

539
00:32:47,990 --> 00:32:48,990
Come with me.

540
00:32:48,990 --> 00:32:50,360
We need to talk.

541
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:15,270
<i>Virtuous and Noble</i>

542
00:33:15,270 --> 00:33:16,360
Sheng,

543
00:33:16,990 --> 00:33:18,870
are you sure about this?

544
00:33:18,870 --> 00:33:19,870
Aunt,

545
00:33:20,150 --> 00:33:21,870
Yin Pei has caused too much damage,

546
00:33:21,870 --> 00:33:23,510
including the death
of Taoist Priest Chongxiao.

547
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,630
I cannot

548
00:33:24,630 --> 00:33:26,560
let him go for what it’s worth.

549
00:33:26,560 --> 00:33:27,990
Yin Pei

550
00:33:27,990 --> 00:33:30,230
is a strong rival.

551
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:32,360
Be extra careful.

552
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:34,080
I will.

553
00:33:34,080 --> 00:33:35,750
I’ve taken your advice

554
00:33:35,750 --> 00:33:36,840
and arranged everything.

555
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:37,560
And

556
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:40,110
Madam Nichang
and the others will help me.

557
00:33:40,110 --> 00:33:41,440
Everything will be fine.

558
00:33:42,150 --> 00:33:44,270
Eliminating him

559
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:46,390
is the right thing to do.

560
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:49,840
Have you seen Fei?

561
00:33:51,110 --> 00:33:52,750
Not recently.

562
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:54,800
She’s probably in Penglai

563
00:33:54,800 --> 00:33:56,320
with Xie Yun.

564
00:34:00,510 --> 00:34:02,200
You kids are old enough

565
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:04,230
to leave the nest.

566
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:46,640
Chuchu.

567
00:34:46,990 --> 00:34:48,640
You startled me.

568
00:34:49,470 --> 00:34:50,510
Chuchu,

569
00:34:50,510 --> 00:34:51,990
do you know

570
00:34:51,990 --> 00:34:52,930
Sheng’s leaving?

571
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,120
Why?

572
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:59,670
He seems to be invited to some banquet.

573
00:34:59,670 --> 00:35:02,320
And he won’t take me with him.

574
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:07,840
The host is Lord Liu of Liu’s Manor.

575
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,190
Lord Liu?

576
00:35:11,030 --> 00:35:13,360
The one of Mount Tai Sect?

577
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,750
How do you know?

